			>
			<DIV>my personal view: post 60 hte plat isnt an issue. its easy to repalce.</DIV>
<DIV>pre 60 it can hurt due to the excessive cost vs loot you gain per grind hour etc.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>now, if a cleric could cast individual spells, and swap mana for dots, then i would be happy. clerics would have a way around the cost if they needed to (ie crs) and could pay the cost when it brings them a better total return (ie group spells)</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>yes i think it sucks that druids got a better type one spell, and I'd love for this to be rebalanced to give clerics the edge in hp, but in total power druids would still be better due to mana regen.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>yes, shaman get focus, which has never had a component cost. I agree with that since its smaller than symbol.&nbsp; </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>we are doin ok, we have had the same cost since 49, cant complain too much there at least. but it would be nice for the single target spells to lose their cost, or for just the symbol line to lose its cost, but the ageo line to keep it.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>to me its one or the other, both is just being greedy.</DIV>
