			<DIV>
<HR>
</DIV>
<DIV>"The crux of the question: Ky - can you give us a glimpse of what the Devs have in store for balancing or modifying the Cleric class? Even just a small slice of information would be better than hanging here and thinking that the Devs have abandonned us... "
<HR>
</DIV>
<P>sometime this or next week the devs will release the summery of our top 10 list, and how they classify each issue on it. sometime after that, hopefully before the release of oow they will release the class definitions. </P>
<P>that process takes time, because they have to finally settle down hard rules that define a class, rather than relying on the more malable flavor text kind of descriptions that have been used until now.</P>
								<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 120; overflow: hidden;">
								
							<A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=411608">Hurk</a><br>~~~~~<br>"Character is always lost when a high ideal is sacrificed on the altar of conformity and popularity." - Anon<br><br>"You can tell the character of someone by how they treat those that can do nothing for them." -Hendrix
